  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Risk of rabies affecting children",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention points out that children under the age of 8 are at the highest risk of contracting mumps.",
        "Foreign media also reported that the center confirmed that two children, including a newborn, were infected with monkeypox.",
        "So far 05 deaths have been reported due to monkeypox in the African region and no deaths have been reported from other countries.",
        "According to the calculations of the World Health Organization, the mortality rate of this disease is stated to be between 3 and 6 percent. (a)"
      ],
